{{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 20''' is the 20th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Shōwa|ja|正和|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1312]] {{ill|April 27|ja|4月27日|qq=}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Ōchō|ja|応長|qq=}} to {{ill|Shōwa|ja|正和|qq=}}. == Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1834]] {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Maehara Issei|ja|前原一誠|qq=}}, a member of the [[Chōshū Domain|長州藩]] (died [[1876]]). * {{ill|Meiji Gannen|ja|明治元年|qq=}} ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1868]] {{ill|April 12|ja|4月12日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Akiyama Masayuki|ja|秋山真之|qq=}}, a naval military personnel (died [[1918]]). == Deaths == * {{ill|Eishō|ja|永承|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1326]] {{ill|April 23|ja|4月23日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kuniyoshi Shinnō|ja|邦良親王|qq=}}, the first prince of {{ill|Go-Nijō Tennō|ja|後二条天皇|qq=}} and the progenitor of the {{ill|Kidera-no-miya|ja|木寺宮家|qq=}} (born [[1300]]). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1604]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kuroda Takakazu|ja|黒田孝高|qq=}}, also known as 【Nyosui】 and 【Kanbei】, a military commander and Christian daimyō (born [[1546]]).
