* {{ill|Meiji Gannen|ja|明治元年|qq=|12=draft}} ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|April 12|ja|4月12日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Akiyama Masayuki|ja|秋山真之|qq=|12=draft}}, a naval military personnel (died [[1918]]).
