秋山真之|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Akiyama Masayuki|qq=}}, a naval military personnel (died [[1918]]). == Deaths == * {{ill|Eishō|ja|永承|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eishō|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1326]] {{ill|April 23|ja|4月23日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 23|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kuniyoshi Shinnō|ja|邦良親王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuniyoshi Shinnō|qq=}}, the first prince of {{ill|Go-Nijō Tennō|ja|後二条天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Go-Nijō Tennō|qq=}} and the progenitor of the {{ill|Kidera-no-miya|ja|木寺宮家|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kidera-no-miya|qq=}} (born [[1300]]). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1604]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 19|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kuroda Takakazu|ja|黒田孝高|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroda Takakazu|qq=}}, also known as 【Nyosui】 and 【Kanbei】, a military commander and Christian daimyō (born [[1546]]).
