== Events == * [[:en:Shōwa (1312–1317)|Shōwa]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1312|1312]] [[:en:April 27|April 27]]) – The era name was changed from [[:en:Ōchō|Ōchō]] to [[:en:Shōwa (1312–1317)|Shōwa]]. == Births == * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 5th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1834|1834]] [[:en:April 28|April 28]]) – {{ill|Maehara Issei|ja|前原一誠|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maehara Issei|qq=}}, a member of the [[:en:Chōshū Domain|長州藩]] (died [[:en:1876|1876]]). * {{ill|Meiji Gannen|ja|明治元年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji Gannen|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1868年|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1868年}} ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1868|1868]] [[:en:April 12|April 12]]) – [[:en:Akiyama Saneyuki|Akiyama Masayuki]], a naval military personnel (died [[:en:1918|1918]]). == Deaths == * [[:en:Eishō (Heian period)|Eishō]] 6th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1326|1326]] [[:en:April 23|April 23]]) – {{ill|Kuniyoshi Shinnō|ja|邦良親王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuniyoshi Shinnō|qq=}}, the first prince of [[:en:Emperor Go-Nijō|Go-Nijō Tennō]] and the progenitor of the {{ill|Kidera-no-miya|ja|木寺宮家|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kidera-no-miya|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 木寺宮|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 木寺宮}} (born [[:en:1300|1300]]). * [[:en:Keichō|Keichō]] 9th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1604|1604]] [[:en:April 19|April 19]]) – [[:en:Kuroda Yoshitaka|Kuroda Takakazu]], also known as 【Nyosui】 and 【Kanbei】, a military commander and Christian daimyō (born [[:en:1546|1546]]).
