'''March 20''' is the 20th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Butsumetsu|1=Butsumetsu|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q10886789}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Shōwa (1312–1317)|en|Shōwa (1312–1317)|qid=Q1324807|lt=Shōwa|1=Shōwa (1312–1317)}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1312|en|1312|qid=Q5734|lt=1312|1=1312}} {{ill|April 27|en|April 27|qid=Q2533|lt=April 27|1=April 27}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Ōchō|en|Ōchō|qid=Q1327136|lt=Ōchō|1=Ōchō}} to {{ill|Shōwa (1312–1317)|en|Shōwa (1312–1317)|qid=Q1324807|lt=Shōwa|1=Shōwa (1312–1317)}}.
== Births ==
* {{ill|Tenpō|en|Tenpō|qid=Q1369045|lt=Tenpō|1=Tenpō}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1834|en|1834|qid=Q7591|lt=1834|1=1834}} {{ill|April 28|en|April 28|qid=Q2534|lt=April 28|1=April 28}}) – {{ill|Maehara Issei|ja|前原一誠|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maehara Issei|1=Maebara Issei|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11397057}}, a member of the {{ill|Chōshū Domain|en|Chōshū Domain|qid=Q876267|lt=長州藩|1=Chōshū Domain}} (died {{ill|1876|en|1876|qid=Q7766|lt=1876|1=1876}}).
* {{ill|Meiji Gannen|ja|明治元年|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji Gannen|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1868年|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1868年|1=1868|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q7717}} ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1868|en|1868|qid=Q7717|lt=1868|1=1868}} {{ill|April 12|en|April 12|qid=Q2499|lt=April 12|1=April 12}}) – {{ill|Akiyama Saneyuki|en|Akiyama Saneyuki|qid=Q709211|lt=Akiyama Masayuki|1=Akiyama Saneyuki}}, a naval military personnel (died {{ill|1918|en|1918|qid=Q2094|lt=1918|1=1918}}).
== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Eishō (Heian period)|en|Eishō (Heian period)|qid=Q1193549|lt=Eishō|1=Eishō (Heian period)}} 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1326|en|1326|qid=Q5782|lt=1326|1=1326}} {{ill|April 23|en|April 23|qid=Q2527|lt=April 23|1=April 23}}) – {{ill|Kuniyoshi Shinnō|ja|邦良親王|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuniyoshi Shinnō|1=Kuniyoshi-shinnō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11643008}}, the first prince of {{ill|Emperor Go-Nijō|en|Emperor Go-Nijō|qid=Q374075|lt=Go-Nijō Tennō|1=Emperor Go-Nijō}} and the progenitor of the {{ill|Kidera-no-miya|ja|木寺宮家|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kidera-no-miya|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 木寺宮|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 木寺宮|1=Kidera-no-miya|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11518293}} (born {{ill|1300|en|1300|qid=Q5609|lt=1300|1=1300}}).
